      <title>由于对反弹的怀疑，对冲基金加大了看跌日元的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/hedge-funds-boost-bearish-bets-on-yen-to-most-in-19-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测日元近期反弹将是短暂的，对冲基金上周将日元看跌押注提高至 2022 年 4 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/hedge-funds-boost-bearish-bets-on-yen-to-most-in-19-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 00:53:11 GMT</pubDate>
