    <item>
      <title>VanEck 的 Hannah 对 Origin 股东投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-04/vanguard-s-wang-on-asia-economic-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[VanEck 投资和资本市场副主管 Jamie Hannah 讨论了他对 Origins 股东投票的期望，他们将就由 Brookfield 和 EIG 能源合作伙伴牵头的财团进行 126 亿美元的收购进行投票。他在“澳大利亚黎明”节目中与海迪·斯特劳德-瓦茨进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-04/vanguard-s-wang-on-asia-economic-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 00:26:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德 128 亿美元的 Origin 收购要约被投资者拒绝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/brookfield-set-for-12-8-billion-snub-as-origin-investors-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Origin Energy Ltd. 股东以微弱优势投票否决了 Brookfield Asset Management Ltd. 牵头的 191 亿澳元（128 亿美元）收购案，此前该基金对一家对澳大利亚能源转型至关重要的公用事业公司进行了一年的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/brookfield-set-for-12-8-billion-snub-as-origin-investors-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鸽派言论推动现货黄金上涨至创纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/spot-gold-rises-to-record-2-091-73-ounce-on-dovish-fed-remarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美联储试图缓和乐观情绪，但由于人们对美国明年初降息的预期不断增强，金价突破了疫情期间创下的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/spot-gold-rises-to-record-2-091-73-ounce-on-dovish-fed-remarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金下跌，美国国债下跌，股市涨跌互现：市场收尾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-us-shrugs-off-powell-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，美国国债下跌，黄金从盘中高点下跌，市场回吐了周五的一些走势，而美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）提醒政策制定者并不急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-us-shrugs-off-powell-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 22:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
